-- üåà RENX HUB UI ‚Äì Full ch·ª©c nƒÉng + giao di·ªán vi·ªÅn 7 m√†u + n√∫t tr√≤n b·∫≠t/t·∫Øt
local plr = game:GetService("Players").LocalPlayer
local cam = workspace.CurrentCamera
local vu = game:GetService("VirtualUser")
local rs = game:GetService("RunService")
local uis = game:GetService("UserInputService")

--== GUI ch√≠nh ==--
local gui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
gui.Name = "RENXHUBUI"
gui.Parent = plr:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")
gui.ResetOnSpawn = false

--== Khung ch√≠nh ==--
local f = Instance.new("Frame", gui)
f.Size = UDim2.new(0, 270, 0, 250)
f.Position = UDim2.new(0, 40, 0, 40)
f.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(15, 15, 15)
f.BackgroundTransparency = 0.4
f.Active = true
f.Draggable = true
Instance.new("UICorner", f).CornerRadius = UDim.new(0, 12)

-- Vi·ªÅn 7 m√†u üåà
local border = Instance.new("UIStroke", f)
border.Thickness = 2.5
task.spawn(function()
	local hue = 0
	while task.wait(0.02) do
		hue = (hue + 1) % 360
		border.Color = Color3.fromHSV(hue / 360, 1, 1)
	end
end)

